bonsaimind.org
==============

This is the source code for the [bonsaimind.org](https://www.bonsaimind.org)
website. It is a Markdown document which is converted to HTML with
[Pandoc](https://pandoc.org/).


License
-------

The build script (`build.sh`), the Lua filter (`processing/filter.lua`) and
the template file (`processing/index.template`) can be considered to be under
CC0 or Public Domain.

The index file (`content/index.markdown`) has to be considered
"All Rights Reserved", with the exception of cloning this repository, and being
edited for the purpose of merging these changes back.

The avatar (`content/avatar.png`) and logo (`content/logo.svg`) have to be
considered "All Rights Reserved" with the exception of cloning this repository.
However, modifications or reuse of these two files are not allowed.

The icons (`content/icons.svg`) is a SVG sprite with icons from
[Font Awesome](https://github.com/FortAwesome/Font-Awesome), see the attached
license file for further details.

The Pandoc](https://pandoc.org/) executable (`processing/pandoc-linux-x64') is
the pre-built release package from
the [Pandoc release site](https://github.com/jgm/pandoc/releases/) and is
licenses under the GPLv2+.


Build
-----

Run the build script to generate the website.
